[*] [b]Coordinates:[/b] X: -1984.43, Y: -1027.10, Z: 7.63
[*] [b]Directions:[/b] Facing the 'Ventura & Skyline' fast travel terminal, turn left and head down the street, turn right at the intersection and contiue on straight into the alley at the end of the street. The shard is at an NCPD: Assault in Progress on Ford Street.
[/list]

[line]

