[*] [b][color=#e06666]Requirements[/color]:[/b] Gimme Danger (Can be looted before the mission)
[*] [b]Directions:[/b] Inside the Arasaka Industrial Park. Can be found in a kit box on the top floor of the central Command Tower during the 'Gimme Danger' main quest.
[/list]

[line]

[color=#ffff00][size=4][b]Santo Domingo - Rancho Coronado[/b][/size][/color]
[b][color=#00ffff]Rancho Coronado (Garage)[/color][/b]
[list]
