[*] [b]Coordinates:[/b] X: 641.66, Y: -2166.40, Z: 38.89
[*] [b][color=#e06666]Requirements[/color]:[/b] Reported Crime: Welcome to Night City
[*] [b]Directions:[/b] From the 'Rancho Coronado East' fast travel terminal, follow the road down to the north-west to a house with wrecked cars outside. Start the 'Reported Crime: Welcome to Night City' by looting the body in the shack outside. The garage with the shard will only open once this quest is active.
[/list]

[line]

[color=#ffff00][size=4][b]Santo Domingo - Arroyo[/b][/size][/color]
