[*] [b]Directions:[/b] From the Edgewood Farm fast travel terminal, follow the road north-west to the second billboard. There will be tire tracks leading off the road to the left. Look for a crashed car with a drone flying around it. The shard is on the body of Darius Loaf.
[/list]

[line]

[color=#ffff00][size=4][b]Badlands - Rocky Ridge[/b][/size][/color]
[b][color=#00ffff]Badlands (Wraith Camp)[/color][/b]
