[*] [b]Directions:[/b] Can be purchased from the Junk Shop vendor (run by Marcin Iwinski and Michal Kicinsky) inside the EBM Petrochem Stadium market. The shard is named '72h Extreme Sensory Deprivation' and costs ~17,000 eddies.
[/list]

